

    font_face

    this standard setting of Sublime Text also sets the font face of the sidebar

    monokai_pro_minimal

    makes the background of the sidebar and main screen the same color (default: false)

    monokai_pro_file_icons

    enables file icons (default: true)

    monokai_pro_file_icons_monochrome

    makes the file icons monochrome (default: false)

    monokai_pro_highlight_open_folders

    highlights open folders in the sidebar (default: false)

    monokai_pro_sidebar_row_padding

    sets the padding between rows in the sidebar (default: 3)

    monokai_pro_sidebar_font_size

    overrides the standard font size of the sidebar (default: 12)

    monokai_pro_label_font_size

    overrides the standard font size of the labels (default: 12)

    monokai_pro_sidebar_lighter

    makes the file names of the sidebar a bit lighter (default: false)

    monokai_pro_small_scrollbar

    makes the scrollbar more of an indicator, useful if you never grab it anyway (default: false)

    monokai_pro_ui_font_face

    overrides the font face of the sidebar, file tabs and button labels

    monokai_pro_style_title_bar

    styles the app title bar in matching monokai pro colors (default: false)

    monokai_pro_panel_font_size

    determines the font size of the quick panels (default: determined by Sublime Text)

    monokai_pro_sidebar_headings

    show headings of groups in the sidebar (default: false)

